From Paul Nakada Subject Eating and Riding was Re Drinking and Riding What's the feeling about eating and riding I went out riding this weekend and got a little carried away with some pecan The whole ride back I felt I was certainly much more alert on the ride I'm sure others have the same feeling but the strangest thing is that eating is usually the turnaround point of weekend From now on a little snack will I'd much rather have a get that full sluggish feeling closer to Paul Paul Nakada Oracle Corporation DoD ' '